datasem.xtext.kanban.domainmodel.kanbanmodel

Interface WorkItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WorkItemImpl

    public interface WorkItem
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Work Item'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Type
    • Description
    • Has Predecessors
    • PTasks
    • Has Subtasks
    • STasks
    • Required Analysis
    • Required Services
    • Maturity Levels
    • Uncertainty
    • Risk
    • Has Impacts
    • Impacts
    • Value
    • Class Of Service
    • Work Source
    • Arrival Time
    • Due Date
    • Id

    See Also:
    KanbanmodelPackage.getWorkItem()
